        <https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/E39PBJt8p3GDkhpJkC9y6FY3wC> ;
    bf:tableOfContents [ a bf:TableOfContents ;
            rdfs:label "Sheet 1 -- Geologic Folio No. 51, Topography of Big Trees and Dardanelles Quadrangles (1907), U.S. Geological Survey (scale 1/125,500) 70 x 44 cm with hand drawings overlaying to show the convergence of four watersheds, largest to smallest: the Middle Fork, Relief, Kennedy's Lake and Lower Kennedy's Meadow Watersheds). -- Sheet 2 -- Drawing A-11-S1, Mass Curve for Run-off of Relief and Kennedy's Lake Watersheds for Seasonal Years 1896 to 1909 showing also a required maximum storage, on graph paper 84 x 54 cm, showing three curves: 1896-1900, 1902-1906, 1906-1909. -- Sheet 3 -- Drawing A-11-S2, Mass Curve for Run-off of Kennedy's Meadow Watershed for Seasonal Years 1896 to 1909 corrections are made to the waters overflowed into the watershed from Relief and Kennedy's Meadows, on graph paper 84 x 54 cm, showing four curves: 1899-1901, 1902-1903, 1904-1905, 1906-1908. -- Sheet 4 -- Drawing A-11-S3, Mass Curve for Run-off of Lower Kennedy's Meadow Watershed for Seasonal Years 1896 to 1909 determining maximum storage required in the reservoir to sustain a reasonable drought, on graph paper 84 x 54 cm, showing four curves: 1896-1900, 1901-1902, 1903-1906, 1907-1909. -- Sheet 5 -- Drawing A-11-S4 Ripll curve, lower Kennedy's meadow, Kennedy's meadow, Kennedy's lake, and relief reservoirs -- Sheet 6 -- Drawing A-12-S1, Stanislaus River Power Projects, Kennedy's Lake Reservoir (scale 1\"=895') and Relief Reservoir (scale 1\"=370') on quality vellum 81 x 77 cm. -- Sheet 7 -- Drawing A-12-S2, Stanislaus River Power Project, Kennedy Meadows Reservoir (scale 3/8\"=100') on quality vellum 76 x 61 cm. -- Sheet 8 -- Stanislaus River Power Project, Series of drawings and charts: Relief rock fill dam, Kennedy's Lake masonry dam, Kennedy Meadows rock fill dam, and Outlet Tower (on quality vellum) 183 x 77 cm. -- Sheet 9 -- Stanislaus River Power Project, Power House (on quality vellum) 90 x 78 cm." ] ;
    bf:title [ a bf:Title ;
            rdfs:label "[Maps and drawings for the Stanislaus River Power Project]." ;
            bflc:nonSortNum "0" ;
            bf:mainTitle "[Maps and drawings for the Stanislaus River Power Project]." ] .

